    public class SearchRequestProvider<RT extends org.gbif.api.model.common.search.SearchRequest<P>,P extends Enum<?> & org.gbif.api.model.common.search.SearchParameter>
extends com.sun.jersey.server.impl.inject.AbstractHttpContextInjectable<RT>
implements com.sun.jersey.spi.inject.InjectableProvider<javax.ws.rs.core.Context,Type>
    Provider class that transforms a set of HTTP parameters into a SearchRequest class instance. This assumes the existence of the following parameters in the HTTP request: 'page_size', 'offset', 'q' and any of the search parameter enum member names case insensitively.
